text: Terrebonne Parish ( ; French: Paroisse de Terrebonne) is a parish located in the southern part of the U.S. state of Louisiana. As of the 2020 census, the population was 109,580. The parish seat is Houma. The parish was founded in 1822. ==References== Category:1822 establishments in the United States Category:1820s establishments in Louisiana
title: Terrebonne Parish, Louisiana
